WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:04.000
Not all applicants will have the opportunity to participate in an admissions interview

00:05.000 --> 00:08.000
Select applicants will be invited to meet with members of the admissions committee during one of the Candidate Weekends, which will take place in Abu Dhabi

00:09.000 --> 00:12.000
All eligible candidates will be contacted by NYU Abu Dhabi to arrange for this visit

00:13.000 --> 00:16.000
Whenever possible, we encourage all applicants to visit the NYU Abu Dhabi campus or attend an information session in their city or region

